      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky. REPLACE THE ACE (3) went forward and gave a great sight beaten a whisker over 1600m at Rockhampton. He's won 2/3 this course and distance and on a 7-day return will use the inside gate to advantage. SAN JUAN (6) settled back from an awkward barrier in the same contest. He'd been narrowly beaten at Townsville prior over 1609m and went close at Rockhampton the one before. Has his first track and trip and expect it to suit. CASH ARTIST (4) led them up and won a 60 here over 2000m. He will run it out and is in the mix. KAYLEEN'S PROFIT (5) was heavily bet in the same contest and lost the rider. She maps well and will also be around the mark.",
